reviewText: this dvd is truly for discussion and humor across the board and would recommend it to one and all.
I did not get this for myself....it was a purchase for my brothers birthday....I assume that he is an avid watcher of O'Reilly.  Sorry, I can't give you 5 stars for myself, but would for my brother.

I had to return the product because the person I bought it for already had one.  This comany was great.  No problem returning my money and the customer service was phenomenal.  Will definately order from them in the future!

That was not what I was expecting out of these guys.  I would have never guessed that Bill O'reilly and Glenn Beck could have actually been funny.  I haven't laughed that hard in a while.

I would reccomend this movie to anyone who likes political humor from a conservative standpoint.
Bill O'Reilly / Glenn Beck Bold & Fresh Tour 2010 DVD Great DVD. I had been curious about their tour....was so much fun to see this video!! We haven't laughed so hard in years..Be sure to get it ....
